overview:
I am Dj da Silva from FABULOS MEDIA ENTERTERPRISE AND PRODUCTION STUDIO FROM SOUTH AFRICA Province NORTH WEST IN RUSTENBURG.I am the owner and the music producer and also do work in all my business departments.

Dj Da Silva is one of best dj’s and music producers in South Africa,he started his music career in 1999 by writting song he then continued as a singer and finally a music producer.

In 2006 he then started his media company mentioned above Fabulous Media Enterprise and Production Sudio well known as FAME PRO STUDIO.Dj da silva does not work alone he woks with two business partners goes with the name of Dj Slots and Dj Century.

FAME PRO STUDIO produce generes like HOUSE,KWAITO,AFRO-POP,HIP HOP,R & B,GOSPEL,SOUL,CLASSIC,TRADITIONAL MUSIC AND MANY MORE.The company is one of the studios that mostly youth and adult music and has found its feet in south african music industry because of its style and unique sound that u can not find elsewhere in the country.

We as owners of FAME PRO STUDIO we build our company under a client satisfaction rule that we believe it is our key to success.We intend making simple and the easiest ways for our artist to sell thier music and video abroad without finding any dificulties,because we realised that popularity is what matters in this buainess.
